---
globs: *.tsx,*.ts,package.json
alwaysApply: false
---

Stack:
- pnpm
- TypeScript
- Expo
- swr for data-fetching
- react-redux for global state _if needed_, else feel free to omit it
  - if we're using react-redux, consider using react-native-mmkv (see https://github.com/mrousavy/react-native-mmkv)
- Expo Secure Store to store auth tokens
- Expo Router for navigation

No design library please (except for things like reanimated which is needed to easily do animations). Implement and style components like Buttons yourself.